ople publications research other pages events of interest life stories of lithuanian women 1945 1970 adopting and remembering soviet reality dalia marcinkeviciene pdf+ into the current burma's political prisoners bo kyi jeanne hallacy larry diamond remembering the gulag varlam shalamov's poetics of memory franziska thun hohenstein audio+ the logic of confrontation and negotiation in democracy reflections of a japanese government lawyer of 40 years akio harada support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 4581 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
